Examples ofcorrectcode for this rule with the"never"option:

/*eslint function-call-argument-newline: ["error", "never"]*/

foo("one", "two", "three");
// or
foo(
    "one", "two", "three"
);

bar("one", "two", { one: 1, two: 2 });
// or
